name: TRONKEY
description: The Donkey on TRON taking us to the sun. TRONKEY combines a love for Donkeys and the TRON Blockchain, launched by an experienced team with deep expertise within Blockchain Technology, cryptocurrency and community building. Inspired by the exciting potential of Meme coins on TRON, and the fast growing communities forming, Tronkey plans to build one of the strongest communities within the Web3 Space.
